                        li.lead.mb-1 Easy Customization.
                        li.lead.mb-1 SASS files included (more customization).
                        li.lead.mb-1 Premium Support.
                        
                        
                
                // HTML SECTION
                section.bg-light.mb-5#html
                    +heading('HTML Structure', 'HTML Structure', 'HTML', 'mb-3')
                    p.lead.mb-5 Italiano is fully responsive HTML5 Template followed HTML5 Structure. Every section is seperated with Comments.
                    
                    h6 Template includes 25 pages, they are:
                    
