                section.bg-light.mb-5#fonts
                    +heading('Fonts', 'Google Fonts', 'Fonts', 'mb-4')
                    
                    p.lead.mb-4 We're using typefaces of Google Fonts which are free for commercial use, and you will not have any troubles with licensing. Also, the fonts are easy to implement on your website, so no trouble with font embedding. These font are:
                    
                    ol.p-0.custom-numbers.mb-0
                        li.mb-1
